data.description: High quality and exquisite home in Pheasant Run. This home has been cared for and updated throughout.  It’s an entertainer’s dream with an expansive main level floorplan, equipped with a large updated gourmet kitchen, 2-story family room with floor-to-ceiling windows, bar area, & a private office/study and new carpet throughout. The second-floor features 5 bedrooms and two full baths. Carry your entertainment outside to the large patio with a built-in grill and a new maintenance-free fence or enjoy the full basement with an updated media room, recreational area and an abundance of storage.
